 debate!</dd> <dd class="tool clearfix"> <!-- assetVote: --> <!-- logged in: --> <!-- remember me: --> <a class="reply needsReg">Reply to this comment</a> <a class="mail toolTipElement2 needsReg" title="E-mail to a friend"></a> <a class="repo toolTipElement2 needsReg" title="Report offensive content"></a> <a class="link toolTipElement2" href="/8618-18567_162-4828659.html?assetTypeId=30&messageId=10353441" title="Permalink to this comment"></a> </dd> <dd class="toolstretch"><!-- --></dd> </dl> <!-- --> <a name="9913348"></a> <dl messageid="9913348"> <dt class="subj"></dt> <dt class="author"> <span>by <b>jopulgo</b></span> October 2, 2010 8:06 AM EDT </dt> <dd id="body_9913348">save billions of dollares on the war on drugs, save billions of dollares by keeping the people out of jail, make billions of dollares by taxing it and create jobs. sounds good to me, let the people have a choice instead of alcohol, tobbaco, and prescription drugs all of which have more harmful side affects . god bless america and the freedom of choice.</dd> <dd class="tool clearfix"> <!-- assetVote: --> <!-- logged in: --> <!-- remember me: --> <a class="reply needsReg">Reply to this comment</a> <a class="mail toolTipElement2 needsReg" title="E-mail to a friend"></a> <a class="repo toolTipElement2 needsReg" title="Report offensive content"></a> <a class="link toolTipElement2" href="/8618-18567_162-4828659.html?assetTypeId=30&messageId=9913348" title="Permalink to this comment"></a> </dd> <dd class="toolstretch"><!-- --></dd> </dl> <!-- --> <a name="9901663"></a> <dl messageid="9901663"> <dt class="subj"></dt> <dt class="author"> <span>by <b>Cqman</b></span> September 28, 2010 11:17 PM EDT </dt> <dd id="body_9901663">Did you know that when the first 13 colonys became about settlers were required to grow Marijuanna. Marijuanna is not a drug but simply a plant, yes you do get high off it but you have been lied to about weed so you wouln't find the good in it. Therefore you see it as a drug no matt